description:
Inside ROG Xbox Ally is an educational video series designed to highlight platform-centric benefits—like Default Gaming Profiles—so players can unlock the full potential of their ROG Xbox Ally.
 
Default Game Profiles: available in preview starting 11/25/25, automatically balance frame rate (FPS) and power consumption for 70 supported games at launch including Fortnite, Gears of War: Reloaded, and Hollow Knight: Silksong, with more coming soon. This means smooth, enjoyable gameplay and extended battery life, without requiring manual adjustments.
 
Learn more:https://www.xbox.com/handhelds/rog-xbox-ally
 
Default Game Profile (Preview) available with select games only. Feature is automatically enabled in game settings. Requires internet connection (ISP fees apply). Products may not be available in all markets. Images are illustrative. See specification pages for details. Device specifications vary by model and are subject to change.

author: Xbox
description:
Here comes the boss—Art of Fighting's Mr. Big weaves a new legend in Fatal Fury!

New DLC character Mr. Big rolls into FATAL FURY: City of the Wolves on December 9!
 
■ Mr. Big (Voice Actors: Marc Graue)
Ruthless ruler of Port Town. With the late Geese Howard long gone, he now aims to take South Town for himself—and, with Rock's sickly mother under his watchful eye, no blood relation or rival power player can do a thing about it. Though the years have grayed him, the name ""Big"" retains its lethal luster; indeed, all who dare underestimate this boss of a man still earn themselves a one-way ticket to a very unhappy end.
